parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure can cause the vehicle to stall, jerk, or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
StabilTrak and traction control system failures can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or reduce speed suddenly, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: StabilTrak and traction control warning lights

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Electrical system failures can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden and unexpected behavior, leading to accidents or loss of control.
Clutch and hydraulic system failures can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or experience sudden and unexpected behavior, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the steering wheel to lock, making it difficult or impossible to steer, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: squealing noise from the power steering pump

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Stabilitrak and Traction Control System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak and Traction Control System can cause the vehicle to lose power, stability, and control, leading to accidents or loss of control.
The failure of the ignition switch can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
and loss of power to accessories.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can lead to the deployment of airbags in non-crash situations, or the failure to deploy airbags in crash situations, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The "Service Air Bag" or "Service Side Detection System" warning light appears on the dashboard
the airbag warning light comes on and stays on
the airbag warning light comes on and off intermittently
the passenger airbag light comes on
the blind spot detection system lights come on and stay on
the key fob does not work
the engine temperature gauge does not work properly.
